Package eu.mais_h.mathsync

Java synchronization library.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BucketSelector
    Selects buckets to store items in.
    Difference<T>
    Represents the difference between two states.
    Resolver<T>
    Computes the difference between two states.
    Summarizer
    Producer of summaries at different levels of detail.
    SummarizerFromJson.Function
    De-generified/simplified backport of java.util.function.Function.
    SummarizerFromLarge.Supplier
    De-generified/simplified backport of java.util.function.Supplier.
    Summary  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PadAndHashBucketSelector
    Pads content and hashes it to select buckets.
    ResolverFromSummarizers<T>
    Resolver using two summarizers to compute the delta.
    SummarizerFromItems
    Summarizer which iterates on items in the current state to build summaries.
    SummarizerFromJson
    Summarizer which deserializes JSON payloads from a remote source.
    SummarizerFromLarge
    Summarizer which uses a large (possibly cached) summary to generate smaller ones.
